ygData.msgSnippet: Nice to meet you!  I ve heard some good things about people on the Cazic server.  wow, Guild Leader... that s a big job, isn t it?  I wish you the best of luck
ygData.messageBody:
Nice to meet you! I've heard some good things about
people on the Cazic server. wow, Guild Leader...
that's a big job, isn't it? I wish you the best of
luck getting Rage, I love seeing people get their
epics. There is so much hard work that goes into it.

Take care and have a good week also.

Ainthara

--- Denise Fullenwider <d_fullenwider@...>
wrote:
